  "report_markdown": "# 2026 FIFA World Cup — Full Bracket Prediction Report\n\n## Executive Summary\n\nUsing the Elo-Poisson baseline (μ=1.4, neutral) blended ~30/70 with DraftKings 1X2 priors, **Argentina is the predicted champion (~14% lift), defeating France 2-1 in AET** in the Final. Brazil and England are early exits in the QF and SF respectively, while the model highlights five genuine upset-risk R32 ties — most notably **Argentina vs Uruguay (M86)** and **Colombia vs Croatia (M83)**. As Algeria posted in R0: *\"Elo-Poisson baseline (μ=1.4, neutral venue) blended 30/70 with DraftKings 1X2 priors\"* anchors the entire pipeline. Ancelotti flagged: *\"Group I is the clear Group of Death — France, Norway, Senegal, Iraq\"*; the model concurs, projecting France to top the group at ~58%.\n\n---\n\n## All 12 Groups — MD2 + MD3 Predictions\n\nFormat: `Matchup | A% / D% / B% | Most-likely | Top-3 scores`\n\n### Group A (Mexico · South Korea · Czech Republic · South Africa)\n- MD2: South Korea vs Czech Republic → **KOR 0.45 / D 0.28 / CZE 0.27** | 1-1 | (1-1 14.2%, 1-0 12.8%, 0-1 11.4%)\n- MD2: Mexico vs South Africa → **MEX 0.74 / D 0.16 / RSA 0.10** | 2-0 | (2-0 16.8%, 1-0 14.1%, 3-0 9.7%)\n- MD3: **Mexico vs South Korea** → MEX 0.50 / D 0.27 / KOR 0.23 | 1-1 | (1-1 13.1%, 1-0 12.4%, 0-0 8.6%)\n- MD3: Czech Republic vs South Africa → CZE 0.55 / D 0.25 / RSA 0.20 | 1-0 | (1-0 14.6%, 2-0 11.2%, 1-1 9.8%)\n- **Final standings:** 1) Mexico 7pts  2) South Korea 5pts  3) Czech Republic 3pts  4) South Africa 1pt\n\n### Group B (Canada · Switzerland · Qatar · Bosnia and Herzegovina)\n- MD2: Switzerland vs Qatar → SUI 0.68 / D 0.19 / QAT 0.13 | 2-0 | (2-0 15.7%, 1-0 13.4%, 3-0 8.9%)\n- MD2: Canada vs Bosnia → CAN 0.40 / D 0.30 / BIH 0.30 | 1-1 | (1-1 14.8%, 1-0 11.7%, 0-1 10.2%)\n- MD3: **Canada vs Switzerland** → CAN 0.30 / D 0.26 / SUI 0.44 | 1-1 | (1-1 13.5%, 0-1 12.0%, 1-2 8.4%)\n- MD3: Bosnia vs Qatar → BIH 0.50 / D 0.27 / QAT 0.23 | 1-0 | (1-0 14.2%, 2-0 10.6%, 1-1 9.1%)\n- **Final standings:** 1) Switzerland 9pts  2) Bosnia 4pts  3) Canada 3pts  4) Qatar 1pt\n\n### Group C (Brazil · Morocco · Scotland · Haiti)\n- MD2: **Brazil vs Haiti** → BRA 0.86 / D 0.09 / HAI 0.05 | 3-0 | (3-0 18.2%, 2-0 16.4%, 4-0 9.1%)\n- MD2: Morocco vs Scotland → MAR 0.52 / D 0.26 / SCO 0.22 | 1-0 | (1-0 13.8%, 2-1 9.6%, 1-1 8.9%)\n- MD3: **Brazil vs Scotland** → BRA 0.80 / D 0.13 / SCO 0.07 | 2-0 | (2-0 16.9%, 3-0 12.3%, 1-0 11.7%)\n- MD3: **Haiti vs Morocco** → MAR 0.78 / D 0.14 / HAI 0.08 | 2-0 | (2-0 15.4%, 3-0 10.8%, 1-0 10.2%)\n- **Final standings:** 1) Brazil 9pts  2) Morocco 6pts  3) Scotland 3pts  4) Haiti 0pts\n- Bellingham noted: *\"Group C draw is sneaky. Brazil are overwhelming favorites, but Morocco (2022 semifinal pedigree) + Scotland (organized, physical)\"* — confirmed by the runner-up spread (2-goal goal-diff swing for MAR/SCO).\n\n### Group D (USA · Paraguay · Australia · Turkey)\n- MD2: **Paraguay vs Turkey** → PAR 0.38 / D 0.28 / TUR 0.34 | 1-1 | (1-1 13.9%, 1-0 12.1%, 0-1 11.7%)\n- MD2: USA vs Australia → USA 0.55 / D 0.24 / AUS 0.21 | 1-0 | (1-0 14.1%, 2-0 11.8%, 1-1 9.3%)\n- MD3: USA vs Turkey → USA 0.55 / D 0.24 / TUR 0.21 | 2-1 | (2-1 10.4%, 1-0 13.7%, 2-0 9.2%)\n- MD3: Australia vs Paraguay → AUS 0.48 / D 0.27 / PAR 0.25 | 1-0 | (1-0 13.2%, 1-1 10.1%, 2-0 9.7%)\n- **Final standings:** 1) USA 9pts  2) Australia 6pts  3) Paraguay 2pts  4) Turkey 1pt\n\n### Group E (Germany · Ecuador · Ivory Coast · Curaçao)\n- MD2: **Germany vs Ivory Coast** → GER 0.72 / D 0.17 / CIV 0.11 | 2-0 | (2-0 16.1%, 1-0 13.7%, 3-0 9.8%)\n- MD2: **Ecuador vs Curaçao** → ECU 0.78 / D 0.15 / CUR 0.07 | 2-0 | (2-0 16.8%, 3-0 11.4%, 1-0 12.6%)\n- MD3: **Germany vs Ecuador** → GER 0.65 / D 0.21 / ECU 0.14 | 2-1 | (2-1 11.7%, 1-0 13.9%, 2-0 9.4%)\n- MD3: **Ivory Coast vs Curaçao** → CIV 0.66 / D 0.20 / CUR 0.14 | 2-0 | (2-0 14.6%, 1-0 13.2%, 3-0 8.7%)\n- **Final standings:** 1) Germany 9pts  2) Ecuador 6pts  3) Ivory Coast 3pts  4) Curaçao 0pts\n\n### Group F (Ne